      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "If you specify a file name which contains a wildcard character (* or ?),"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "a file selection list is displayed.  You may scroll through the list via"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the UP and DOWN scroll commands or via the LOCATE command, and you may"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "select one file at a time via the SELECT primary command, or the S line"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To return to the entry panel from the file list, enter the END command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For more information on the following topics, select:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "1 + File list  Scrolling"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "2 + File list  Locate"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "3 + File list  Select"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "4 + File list  S line command"
